WEBVTT

00:01:58.712 --> 00:02:01.438
Researcher: But, you know,
I don't see any more treats.

00:02:01.462 --> 00:02:03.114
Will you give one to Monkey?

00:02:04.278 --> 00:02:05.898
Toddler: Yeah.
Researcher: Yeah?

00:02:06.720 --> 00:02:08.181
Toddler: Yeah.

00:02:12.852 --> 00:02:14.008
Here.

00:02:14.032 --> 00:02:17.779
Researcher: Ooh, yummy. Mmmm.

00:02:18.862 --> 00:02:20.495
Toddler: All gone, he ate it.

00:02:22.186 --> 00:02:25.856
Elizabeth Dunn: Now, we trained
research assistants to watch these videos

00:02:25.880 --> 00:02:28.435
and code toddlers' emotional reactions.

00:02:28.459 --> 00:02:30.613
Of course, we didn't tell them
our hypotheses.